Project		: minstack - A minimal stack for UDP and/or TCP transactions
Email		: a_bouin@yahoo.fr
License		: GPLv3
Home Page	: ...

minstack is a GPL v3 library that help the implentation of UDP/TCP trasactions.
It aims to implement a minimal stack with a very simple high layer API.

Features :
----------

minstack has support for :
 - TCP client
 - TCP server

Installation procedure:
-----------------------

The program is known to run on linux.

   $> ./autogen.sh
   $> ./configure
   $> make
   $> su -c 'make install'

Contact information:
--------------------

For more information on minstack, any contributions, or any remarks,
you can contact me at <a_bouin@yahoo.fr>.
